 * T_IRQ (PB2) is read as a plain GPIO_Input (active low).
 * XPT2046_touched() checks GPIO first (fast), then confirms with SPI Z read.
 * Poll interval: 20 ms → worst-case 20 ms touch latency (imperceptible).
 * -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
